titles.title: I Can Run Through A Troup

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
(For by Thee....)
I can run through a troup
And leap over a wall
Alleluia Alleluia
(For by Thee)
I can run through a troup
And leap over a wall
Alleluia Alleluia

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Now there is no condemnation
Jesus is the Lord
Of my salvation
(For by Thee...)
I can run through a troup
And leap over a wall
Alleluia Alleluia
